Package: dann
Title: Discriminant Adaptive Nearest Neighbor Classification
Version: 1.0.3
Authors@R: c(person("Trevor", "Hastie", role = "aut"), person("Gaurav", "Sood", email = "gsood07@gmail.com", role = c("ctb", "cre")))
Description: Implements Discriminant Adaptive Nearest Neighbor classification
    using Trevor Hastie's original Fortran implementation. DANN adapts the
    distance metric based on local discriminant analysis to improve nearest
    neighbor classification, particularly when classes have different
    covariance structures or when irrelevant features are present.
URL: https://github.com/finite-sample/dann, https://finite-sample.github.io/dann/
BugReports: https://github.com/finite-sample/dann/issues
